data.description: Enjoy your own tranquility and peace and quiet on this 4.62 acres at the base of Dug Gap Mountain, Mill Creek area. This contemporary style features large vaulted ceiling den with rock fireplace, open dining room, kitchen with breakfast area, 22x20 living room, 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, master suite has it's own private terrace to enjoy your morning coffee. Relaxing spacious sunroom overlooking a 42x30 deck with a 12x12 gazebo, large glass windows! Home also features 20x28 detached 3-car garage, gated entrance, green house, gardening area, partial concrete driveway. Tons of beautiful wildlife!
